msgid ""
"The first address of a range is the **network address**. It is used to "
"identify networks and to route information from one network to another."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: docs/books/admin_guide/12-network.md:65
msgid ""
"The last address of a range is the **broadcast address**. It is used to "
"broadcast information to all the machines on the network."
