#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/12-network.md:323
msgid "``` BOOTPROTO=dhcp ```"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: docs/books/admin_guide/12-network.md:325
msgid ""
"Specify the MAC address (optional but useful when there are several "
