#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/12-network.md:493
msgid ""
"If the ping does not work, first check the network cable to your network "
"switch and reassemble the interface (see the `if up` command), then check "
"the interface itself."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '3) '
#: docs/books/admin_guide/12-network.md:495
msgid "Validate the connectivity of the gateway"
