#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/12-network.md:623
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"!!! Warning\n"
"    The `netstat` command is now deprecated and is no-longer installed by default on Rocky Linux. You may still find some Linux versions that have it installed, but it is best to move on to using `ss` for everything that you would have used `netstat` for.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/12-network.md:625
msgid ""
"The `netstat` command (**network statistics**) displays the listening ports "
"on the network."
